iklingen vi ser her er helt hinsides, sier Hops\u00f8.", "Han fortviler over m\u00e5ten ungdom jobber flere timer eller dager uten l\u00f8nn, f\u00f8r arbeidsgiveren til slutt sier at det ikke er bruk for dem.", "- Man kan ha pr\u00f8vetid, men da er det en samfunnskontrakt som sier at man f\u00e5r l\u00f8nn for den arbeidskraften man gir, maner han.", "LES OGS\u00c5: Dette f\u00e5r hun 180 kroner i timen for", "LES OGS\u00c5: Sommerpatruljen avdekket mangler"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "jobb"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "cf7fdbff4b9a44d9f414d0385b46957c77131f4434650c815ce4146d0ead58a9"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T09:19:30.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "LOs sommerpatrulje reagerer p\u00e5 utstrakt bruk av \u00abpr\u00f8vejobbing\u00bb i S\u00f8r-Tr\u00f8ndelag."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1398039.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/IMG_Lo_sommerpatrulje_01_1_1_EL3M00P"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/aad84e89170659058577c2d7d18455403ed3c312.jpg?5995802b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Vi f\u00e5r bakoversveis -adressa.no", "Nektes 38 000 kroner", "God utvikling", "Fortviler over \u00abpr\u00f8vejobbing\u00bb"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "aad84e89170659058577c2d7d18455403ed3c312"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["jobb", "ledige stillinger", "deltidsjobb", "sommerjobber", "arbeid"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "jobb,ledige stillinger,deltidsjobb,sommerjobber,arbeid"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "jobb"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "careers"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["l\u00f8nn", "tilfeller", "patruljen", "jobb", "utvikling", "bedriften"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag per olav hops\u00f8"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value":